item.description:
The Fisher Cats will be playing against the Erie
Seawolves at MerchantsAuto.com Stadium. There is a firework
show after the game sponsored by Atlas fireworks. The Fisher
Cats are the double AA affiliate of the Toronto Blue Jays. The tickets are going to cost $12. Please mail your check or money order mailed to Stanley Fonder, 108 Eastern
Avenue, Unit 202, Manchester, NH 03104.
item.how_to_find_us: Stan will post a meeting location for all members who purchase tickets by May 31st.
